<br>
Regardless of how good you think Whirlwind is or not, Hammer would still be better because you would hit just as often and it would be for much greater damage.  And put in the hands of a MT warrior, with much lower avoidance, who wants to get aggro with his riposte disc, this owns. <p><FONT COLOR="#990000"><B><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=7531" target="_blank"><FONT COLOR="#990000">Mateo Esquandolas</FONT></A></B>
